name: Calling Cards
description:
Hate writing your email address on a cocktail napkin?
Tired of not getting your stuff back?

Let me custom design a set of calling cards for you. You'll find that these little cards are an invaluable resource. They're like a business card for your personal life!

50 cards come in a set
Printed on heavy ecru cardstock
Measure 3.5"x2"

Choose any text and any image. Just contact me with the details.

name: The Laughing Tree
description:
75 sheets of white paper featuring a sweet brown tree

loose leaf sheets attached to a matching magnetic clipboard

size: approximately 4.25" x 5.25"

perfect for hanging on the fridge or in your locker to write quick notes or lists

makes a great stocking stuffer!

comes with matching ribbon; packaged in a clear bag

name: Bug Collection Boxed Set
description:
In this wonderful gift set, you'll get 8 dragonfly panel cards with envelopes, 8 bee enclosure cards with envelopes, and 25 butterfly name plates or calling cards.

All text can be modified/moved/removed.

Cards come packaged in a sturdy black paper box with a clear lid. Calling cards are packaged in their own smaller box.

Choose different images to make your own collection! (I've done everything from surfboards to oak trees, so don't think your request will be unreasonable!)

I'll be happy to adjust the price if you want more cards or fewer.

name: Monogrammed Panel Cards
description:
A great expression of simple sophistication.

Printed on ecru cardstock panel cards. Choose any ink color for your monogram.

8 cards with envelopes
approximate size: 4.5"x6.25"

.....

Monograms 101: A quick refresher --

-Center initial always stands for last name.
-For one person, left initial stands for first name; right initial stands for middle name.
-For a couple's monogram, left initial stands for her first name; right initial stands for his first name.

.....

In your Paypal message to the seller, please include the following information:
-Ink color choice
-Initials with clarification
[ex: C (first name); K (middle name); A (last name)]
or
[ex: C (left letter); A (middle letter); K (right letter)]
